The paper deals with video human action classification and detection using deep neural networks, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The proposed network also involves capsule networks, which are a recent development in deep learning and fall under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also deals with video processing and analysis, which falls under the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Finally, the paper involves training the network end-to-end, which involves optimization and learning algorithms, falling under the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-category.
